---
title: Southern Spiced Chicken with Smashed Potatoes and Garlicky Green Beans
description: Warming Southwest spices truly shine in this recipe! Chicken gets the Southern-style breading treatment, and is paired with garlicky green beans, creamy smashed potatoes and a truly delicious gravy! The ultimate comfort food!
